diff:1372722195:1372722037:=19c19,23%0a%3c %0a---%0a> There's not much really to say here that hasn't been said before, but I'll give three guidelines that I ask players to remember:%0a> %0a> * Werewolves are aggressive, and sometimes that seeps into players' mentalities a bit; but remember, the purpose of this is to have fun. Be cool!%0a> * There is no such thing as a bad question. If you don't know something, don't be afraid to ask!%0a> * All feedback is good feedback, as long as it is constructive and polite. If you think we're doing something wrong, don't be afraid to tell us--but please keep it cordial and respectful. We may not agree with you, and when we don't, we will endeavour to be as clear as possible.%0a26,27c30,31%0a%3c For a current updated list of the venue ST [[http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/|TBD]].  %0a%3c %0a---%0a> For a current updated list of the venue ST [[http://www.wantonwicked.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=group&g=1577|please click here]].  You will be able to FPM the ST by clicking their names.%0a> %0a30c34,56%0a%3c %0a---%0a> [[#wfSchedule]]%0a> [++'''Scheduling a Scene'''++]%0a> %0a> To schedule a scene, contact the Werewolf Storytellers, either through your character thread or via Forum PM (message the 3.0 Werewolf ST list).%0a> %0a> [--%25color=#996600%25[[#wftop| Back to top]]--]%0a> %0a> [[#wfChanges]]%0a> [++'''Becoming a Werewolf'''++]%0a> %0a> Only plain ("vanilla") mortals & Wolf-Blooded may First Change. XP spent into the Wolf-Blooded Merit and other associated Merits (e.g. Lunatic Glare) is refunded to the character, but all other supernatural Merits that a Werewolf can't have (e.g. Unseen Senses) are lost without refund.%0a> %0a> The First Change should take place over a month long storyline; ideally it would begin and end on the moon that the PC will Change.%0a> %0a> A newly changed Werewolf gains the following for free:%0a> * Primal Urge 1%0a> * Auspice Renown at level 1%0a> * One level 1 Auspice Gift%0a> * One free Specialty in an Auspice Skill%0a> %0a> The newly-changed Werewolf may also choose, at this time, to purchase Werewolf Merits that are normally ''character creation-only'' (e.g. Auspice Blessing). These are not free, however.%0a> %0a> [--%25color=#996600%25[[#wftop| Back to top]]--]%0a
